                <head>114. Editorial Note</head>
                <p>
                    <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 114/3, “United States Programs for National
                    Security,” June 5, 1952, included Summary Statement No. 7—Foreign Intelligence
                    and Related Activities, prepared by the Central Intelligence Agency. For text of
                    Summary Statement No. 7, see <ref target="frus1952-54v02p1#pg_50">
                        <hi rend="italic">Foreign Relations</hi>, 1952–1954, volume II, Part 1,
                        pages 50</ref>–<ref target="frus1952-54v02p1#pg_53">53</ref>.</p>
            </div>
